<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.7">
<l>kuṭaiyā vilaṅkal koṇṭēnti māri paḻutā niraikāttu</l>
<l>caṭaiyā ṉōṭa vaṭalvāṇaṉ taṭantōḷ tuṇitta talaivaṉiṭam</l>
<l>kuṭiyā vaṇṭu kaḷḷuṇṇak kōla nīlam maṭṭukukkum</l>
<l>puṭaiyār kaḻaṉi yeḻilārum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the leader who, having taken up and held a hill as an umbrella</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the rain became useless, [and] having protected the herd,</l>
<l>Severed the long arms of mighty Bāṇa, so that he with matted locks ran,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi full of color [from] fields on [all] sides</l>
<l>Where nectar pours down from lovely blue lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">so that bees sip honey in swarms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
